model.commissioningModeInitialStepsInstruction:
Network requirements: 
 2.4GHz, IPv6, Bluetooth Permission 
 App/Hub minimum system requirements: 
 1) iOS 16.1, iPad OS 16.1, HomePod OS 16.1, tvOS 16.1, and watchOS 9.1. 
 2) Android O (8.1), Google Home app v2.62, Nest Hub Max v8.20220713.2.194059, and v1.56.324896 for Nest Hub (1st gen), Nest Hub (2nd gen), Nest Mini, Nest Audio, Google Home, and Nest WiFi Pro v1.63.327820. 
 3) Amazon Alexa is not yet supported in the official release. 
 4) Meross iOS app v3.10.0, android app v3.8.1.
model.commissioningModeSecondaryStepsInstructi:
1. Reboot your mobile phone to clear app’s cache. 
 2. Follow user manual to reset the accessory. 
 3. Power cycle the accessory. 
 4. Configure the accessory again.
